/p/AF1QipNzrKpC4k862pwxbR8VRKGbt9bAiNtOaQQeRhJS=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipO5YOvwnjVSwUjO4L7s93SHmn1TJ2QeXevShoM1=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOVZZOpNtySWwaQqs48mXdYSTqAfheoy-4BxLJx=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipO_5hWUeN8qbZFXtpXqS8DkdiRa6S9namUT6ckB=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPAld-xvN3-y4Z8Qm8pBxMQKcwZtT6MrEQfnajW=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPWBVgaOGhdRNQzTiielQFXj17J490O7SLley4I=w203-h120-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPZ5pqNMFgsta-W072ui-ionyiQ_rHIK1ess-26=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPaSNNzlO7uFvNVhD4mQ5hMC_cZ8k2PDYssUgmB=w203-h152-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Monday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Saturday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Sunday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Thursday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Tuesday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Wednesday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Rok Trtnik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWr0-w6ErUTEJ9U7-nxqOo35AVizKtlkZvVUvSLFboTBnud2pnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to pickleball today. Didn’t expect much but it exceeded my expectations. The court was super nice, the owner was lovely. Overall it was a lovely experience and would definitely recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jrgAEKPqUp4ymWFWaiv-cA076nSl6wSgtWIyUGFieGr1CVvIQ13pPrWuq5mqmFqGAWOeWSyO2b_GVoWOp-MZXxacSQ41F5KTP-Ncl0Rp_phHJc28_SmAeAA_nV3bikDh9gOfIePaGsyX3=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn39nybOC7k8l4cTiCvB-RyqNPQ2hDWfgSMx4ZGCzsAgjk4XabZaHi9QL6fGCnMQjVPVAUhhqF_0nud3JpUR9cBag6ZyDg9lmuNrjZUxRYOaEUdLgwmJaL0-DhCK3jj5tmxRMC1MFGewak1g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ZxlFt0ee5T93ZqFZebLTA8Z8FfmWPNgKl9YPQxgMpri8tpgS_1rtFYM6c9Z6Zm2x-9TmYjbJnTDxCX5eXvdIimF__oJBt3dmp9YNil2W88jctIOyrVJCvw-xkkQbeNubJLoAEipMkt8Mq=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-2"},{"Name":"Sarah Bradford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIENdz0kOvshqPZGDwhSNQwhXntfriDsAn3wuyAc2KtnbnJMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my favourite pickleball court to play on in Da Nang! It’s a smaller more intimate setting with only 3 courts so make sure to book in advance. The courts and facilities are in good condition. The staff are friendly, always greeting us kindly and taking good care of us. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maxine B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6B3juYyVsS2sLQnypSDrE5hx_piQqXfkobHKUDiVA-R_RPvn8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is well worth checking out!I\nI was out exploring the area and found this location. It''s new, clean, shaded, in excellent shape. oya lots of parking. The prices are fare.\nAfter playing the kind man gave me Longan :)\nWill be back.💯 👍 😎","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Gtud9Mpaq9Z_bJKmde4O913FcHe_WBURx239ww10Z6pSkNJEuNDYhAdB6ooTLtvNCWYTTCjKAkUSuS1QUFw4Ch8CyVWRbHrOz3Gr-C2QjxHHEYzRzp-qFufjOE6MdKAMB97dZUreDLa0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_BVTMmusjtIH_xS0TeyzQztdw2UKZ9QwLaorkFII3N738BuEcOcSJqgpkrAEw0WsE_N36xHQcKeFmB17_YLduaJbQu1CLOwexE7YAfpE_g6LB6jW3zS8Jq1jDi1KBnGtGsNq9rfFWTKA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2-ISHRtNwvTmWlTLvPt_Q4lCfE41ks5zCjzGbcjGHGaLx9N1Z_-BnfV_Hi-uHrkJdLVG0V1J2N2lsOCWZaSfee8hZW-V82cFceeizGWPvQbby7QP2Q8bqcnPT_nNiMraLN71ZRCa401ZMX=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0k4Sp1liyFxECkZvU4k2Lohfrun5H5bD-aJLpg4rYovQzAGWRqLq-1clzdp0gRkqRTnEO8af4640GGet33-LfzGCSN6OVvzBbYrGsVJ749A6CR2mBxJjoJ41P-ERt20rmJVCu6Ope3ime6=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VvvhfcuWiCRT5qTk-3LJ7c58oj3hQoRTTdnJo6S_qR9UaKcxlPkQjj1dno5YyctDqGJTLOcSfMhBTXsh9yHLh828gtafAer4-eQ6yTwPKevCcFMFx93qzepZJ-x_S4VmD9zOXxXPme4o2=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-9"},{"Name":"JOSEPH LUM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0iSGhGxykrfa7c9auGZp-2vHqB5JO-6OJ7P4uTdVDNO5zxVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Booked court for 9am to 10am...140000vnd  for 1 hr.  Can whstsapp people to look for a 4th.  They serve coffee and tea, also sell some shoes, paddles, balls, over grips..   It''s covered so can play on windy or rainy day.  Or you can join a round Robin group later in the day.  Alternatively you can rent the paddle.  So far we''ve played here at least twice weekly and it''s always been enjoyable.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3yX7xKzkpidjixL7k6M1dhu03ffv1P_37Agxvdg6o6PLiO0jZrfsSHHyhlbZK_UCIU_oKFCr0JmbfK5DqSARMSSOK0jhyRU7x0FhIc1J779HosT5nGRrkf_y2OcbgZ1P3P0fG1=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17b1QgGsrtGMs5fqTh_kSqPrdBqXlsNR56-3eu_wthGuxwUx1x71f7dQc3yvRLCN2vLznm5Nr7JVwsiXJpZey3i0PFOAlaXtMwoUPZcRILVQLbxTJpmtn8kjzBx8wEYy0y3qF-sA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25oO5C4wyvGXsb7VNtwTx_UzoyJ44SJTGG_PyERZFscd8JEprHnSM6lTx_ykG9pUIFiUhJqbjH5NDDeE1D-shRqH-v1iNPffQJ0OmvvfZJsl2N5u4PiD30_qtFXkoYJzsr6bZc=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-7"},{"Name":"Honest Evaluator","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRTHjeBNz0rJxFJvTbab2HJqAOR1IbWS6aCHnECxlIsO4mMD8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Should have better divides between the courts so people aren’t constantly going into one another’s courts to pick up balls!\n\nBalls that are provided with paddles are cracked and not ideal to play with.\n\nQuite hot and no ventilation at the back of the courts.\n\nCourts are more expensive than others around.\n\nTet prices were hugely inflated.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S van der Merwe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNr-w2M8FK1-9Gu5E83Gz7kbL8uARUQzyhkarG9s7-__fsODRVUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Court is good. But rackets were old.\nStaff was friendly -  but cut us off 10min before our 1 hour mark. (We started 11:10) There were no other people waiting to play.  They could have just allowed us to finish the game","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bruce Merit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXLuuUip336NC3Jem3yg885o-TmOoLpovdrevZGmHw72bhndzoXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great courts even has a practice wall! Unfortunately smoking 🚬 area is close to court#1. Retractable roof for shade. Good central location and hours","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raushaniia Polosina-Suleymanova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCNZkHiuHUN4JRNVpAQJpf2miqtSwa-GnRBOdjYfQ2_OOmegWNzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An amazing spot for pickleball in Da Nang! The court is high-quality, with excellent equipment and a well-maintained surface. The staff is super friendly and always welcoming, making every visit a pleasure. Plus, the on-site café surrounded by greenery is the perfect place to relax after a game. A must-visit for pickleball lovers looking for a great atmosphere and top-notch facilities!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn04WaNTWPjSM-ZgjlVeTKKpy73smPbXBdLh_uimpQFKtAqfhnwsftJLj-Z96Bd_pjITx44EGVdA-jNwXpSth3RMPWXpd9NWOmcZCEPsqjdL1b0u6BC02Rv-cS5-GVVcwKfMV9m1=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1veAWnpUqPpeOL52pI0pmE-Aue7rm5d8ETFOkKB4Erb6-r4GDkZA3OlUXNs1zzBogO1eyZm5XtIcYVkjJ_hiTWMaEBCLPOJoQMD7n40mhc4F6qVBEELFwxwECnb1Do54JZdEUQFQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-19"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"4":0,"5":16,"6":19,"7":29,"8":35,"9":38,"10":41,"11":41,"12":43,"13":49,"14":59,"15":66,"16":83,"17":76,"18":73,"19":50,"20":45,"21":38},"Monday":{"4":0,"5":16,"6":25,"7":43,"8":54,"9":62,"10":66,"11":72,"12":73,"13":71,"14":70,"15":75,"16":79,"17":83,"18":74,"19":77,"20":66,"21":61},"Saturday":{"4":