ame":"RED KİT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhiI57ju45vV-r4UB4ntkmoCkg8u5QpcjFCexxSb21918ILAk3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This gym is disturbing everyone in the neighborhood. They don''t care that their customers are shouting loudly at 5:30 in the morning. They don''t care that their neighbors are being disturbed, because money has blinded them. Now, in response to this comment, they''ll probably say that the land used to be a dump and was full of rats, and they''ll defend themselves. If only rats were still roaming the land like they used to be, at least it would remain a quiet, peaceful place. You have no right to disturb anyone. You are committing a crime...These videos were recorded at 5:30 AM.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2WXumN0KkKqYR1mvCnmmUB-E_v7Zy_qyKT-tuJguglAnJlF8404Bvu7PAHMMo49e6hf6gMtuQJyO5Jq4wHdfDEMi2WTc7sjAoOhTb004gijt9MlbFzuyDcOXZv77GqSRjUgRX2Gsqsz3a4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1iCqxJWJ80_r5_oA8mQsu8j0Db9kqANy0CWdzeluZmhTi2nNAziD5Our9i8FB79JD76Ck52PBKdd04SwBsmkYmVdQvKDvN1T5bDUEs_Crg5u_zWvk6FN_2DB7GXAuKwssJDQTEz3RBM5gg=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-13"},{"Name":"Наталья Ромашина","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnydHaCoP5CoTLL_pXIllH8tGhpbyAlHewQOELmJMh0nlq7KcF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The continuous noise from this club is making me crazy.\n\nThe constant popping sound of the game, combined with your players yelling and shouting, is relentless. It feels like a drumming right against our windows at all hours. This is a residential neighborhood, and it''s simply impossible to get any rest or peace.\n\nPls enforce reasonable hours for your games. It is completely unacceptable to have members shouting and generating this constant racket at 5-6 am","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaOrX1hWs6sKlNM3W6qftd0jRUQehRc3Ke4Qz2m-WA9wDw4WU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Your new members scream at the top of their lungs every 5 seconds. It''s maddening. I''m going crazy. I''m ready to pack my things and move to a new apartment. Please control your loud and obnoxious members. It''s a residential area. Edit: contacted owner. Ignored me until I(and some neighbors) left poor reviews, so he finally responded. First time we spoke he seemed interested in finding out who the group was and asking them to stop. We had respectful conversation. Next time they screamed for 2 hours straight I wrote owner and the owner was incredibly hostile and vulgar. Made crazy accusations, lies and insults. Called me disrespectful. Tried telling me he cleaned up a landfill (it was just an empty lot 🤣) and said I was trying to ban him(literally just asked him for help with one group). Said I was sabotaging and harassing him(I wasn''t). The guy is completely unstable and aggressive.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Fj3GEgeTzjoj8YVmHhbye7eyZo151meSc2SHs026UfLExC_6LKPFGFA91AAeavGoVPVoCZcuFXU31hZPvOYUu-Rm-mjVxPilS3q5O6-8MBfL6kt5H5w7TPVRJquTNjA6thFTW=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-4"},{"Name":"Lucia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL257sv8OUvNUWtKctcQCpSQOuFOOwADMVSssoDByqQ0jYRXxk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best place to play pickleball in Da Nang! Extremely clean, rackets for hire, drinks available for purchase & clean toilets. You can easily book courts online or via whatsapp. The staff are also so nice and friendly.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0QcHmhqzL5SA2wi9AqRl6pLRlQ2nUKCMKWajMyA20OG1MF9bMDpVIzOcDZdeYFu_csufM-GQbunDkOfRNuwgbcdu7hat_yTBIyF7iIgHsYQhEC52Gu8KI12U33EqWadkw9O7hKIA=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-24"},{"Name":"Ross Hudson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOiA1QRajIgVsSqD6kMjh7KniABz70nrU55lujSoL0DR76HzM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decent courts but could do with having floor to ceiling dividing nets to stop balls flying across other courts. Slightly cheaper courts elsewhere also, but it is fine.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0nml2TXY_cD9goYs28OTLeMUIZh6tbgR48XK8uIiNhqZUG2nxtNy4wxAb_DFc29nzZUuV3BnQ5nXRKAr3hUZJBpyNVmj94Q_RDzC7p_2mlH6qHy40Y7HIgwUmyBC-9MGJ5cLSB=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-24"},{"Name":"Thảo Nguyễn Thị","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXicvG9paT5U3cAtRjYVIU42QtPPj-AM0CmjieNcnNaEVYQpSY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! Everything is spot on—great atmosphere, friendly service, and affordable pricing. I keep coming back, and for good reason. Definitely worth 5 stars!🤩🤩🤩","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ZGV5QgOAwd0aHxuQfaGGxYO4356juHIgNq2Sh2LwSz5T71wIgemkghYwNpjXdu_W8VdhHQ0ydJ25-GzfpsDyoulx_V-odF64YPCRkTWrwkXHX6rqZEHb9AXUTYTUyYQdrL0v3dQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1HKz5H7-XXyLlLfdFttrT-X8i5bxzJ3k8WRbuIbPLl2GVhAGiVgw1I62z9N2YOXPqUsyoTWE-Y6-_peZsF89t2sJkseIzWi3o2z8wmu7fF1QUNKqyWbLw7T8FctLrhCAiBBb_a=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3GFLtOdWicuDSxQgLpHIFsVYSccPmIDDLnE3iYNuBK3jjlIevvYHPtwNWQIw5TUj5ZxziUxqSiHP3Ev2wJSGLjeVRbyIegOFnOtvhKmDQMsRl-hp2MnzmmbcipB9AwmLuhJZ3gnw=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-2"},{"Name":"Declan Rowlands","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHXim94zq6LXyK10phPqLSIpZxAcMx7nhNSNnzlYYUVitKcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love these courts. 120k/hr through the day, 140k/hr in the evenings. You can rent a racket and borrow balls too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"max","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-wntpdhi0MCaufInJ2zYY2zcWj2s11sGmzTvL5arGNINOos8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The court was nice but kind of small. The staffs were friendly. The one minor problem is the separation net they have. My friend tripped and injured both her knees.\nLike, what the point of that metal thing when you can''t stop the ball from getting into other courts??","Images":null,"When":""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"4":0,"5":16,"6":18,"7":27,"8":37,"9":42,"10":37,"11":32,"12":27,"13":23,"14":24,"15":36,"16":58,"17":87,"18":100,"19":97,"20":71,"21":50},"Monday":{"4":0,"5":15,"6":17,"7":20,"8":31,"9":47,"10":54,"11":49,"12":38,"13":28,"14":25,"15":36,"16":54,"17":78,"18":85,"19":76,"20":49,"21":36},"Saturday":{"4":0,"5":17,"6":23,"7":23,"8":32,"9":44,"10":54,"11":51,"12":47,"13":43,"14":44,"15":47,"16":62,"17":76,"18":80,"19":69,"20":51,"21":35},"Sunday":{"4":0,"5":16,"6":18,"7":27,"8":34,"9":41,"10":41,"11":35,"12":29,"13":22,"14":29,"15":41,"16":57,"17":70,"18":68,"19":65,"20":48,"21":42},"Thursday":{"4":0,"5":17,"6":16,"7":18,"8":22,"9":29,"10":32,"11":29,"12":30,"13":24,"14":32,"15":40,"16":58,"17":71,"18":75,"19":71,"20":64,"21":57},"Tuesday":{"4":0,"5":15,"6":20,"7":20,"8":28,"9":36,"10":48,"11":43,"12":37,"13":29,"14":29,"15":32,"16":51,"17":69,"18":81,"19":76,"20":65,"21":48},"Wednesday":{"4":0,"5":12,"6":15,"7":22,"8":34,"9":45,"10":49,"11":43,"12":35,"13":31,"14":40,"15":49,"16":56,"17":68,"18":74,"19":69,"20":56,"21":41}}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral washroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safe space","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Onsite services', 'Gender-neutral washroom', 'LGBTQ+ friendly', 'Transgender safe space', 'Free parking garage', 'Free parking lot', 'Free street parking', 'On-site parking']::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name