{"Name":"B Peters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAPGRC6mJR-5eA7-mWxn3PU4yLe94ToWiPbqrwiAWObe_iXf9tBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Inexpensive place to play, although not the cleanest facility.  The floors could use a good scrubbing.  The ventilation is just ok, not great as some have reported.  There were some players smoking during warm-up or play.  That was a first for me!  It''s a little arbitrary as to which player(s) go next.  But, I''ve noticed this is the case for many places in Danang.  Overall, decent and we played here a few times while staying in Danang.  The owner is very nice and hospitable!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Claudi Michi Wandervogel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_p8viZTKTH84kzli9ouZq2cuHrTcNkpxiKMaT6XgNY5PvMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Toller Platz. 4 Innen- und 5 Aussenplätze. Sehr freundliche Mitarbeiter und Spieler.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1xkLY-3iRmNFU74ccSh3PhBMyBToTmPkeE6q5pf8D7MwIARkUBJWafF3_6Xj-keVTc2wGKNv95hZLgP2sej7R_CjIyBSGNJb258SxSzPjTotSw-L8nxNNPgIJtxuXrmgD7OcZpmMSXzpFY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3vdXc2cJweS60g0whDDGvb5iJWpvkMExKvHq4oBfrzBkin9VgPIaniETz61bgRc9Zi__P_NfZjAIGLeQ3u7-T9npiKujqfEc4Z1-5ba7OH5lXI7dfTcu9bPLpQqlMqRx8_VqQEa7kYeEO1=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3MKv67HuakNkHypM-EcpPE3ECpO7mkGkRpu9remI27-dB0KcEE8buhP1fO9kyd-3wjT3Upbfnz-6uR5a2-gxoEFIeot50Px-wsuEz__abMXjD_D6GeSsroGvXNL9f70TnXoUV8wEXHOh8=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-23"},{"Name":"Geeta Bhagavati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8fqfxGNyosyTK5C0OyzQDUN_xlVS3IUqxXNMTVCsoWvQAGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Хороший корт. У моря, помещение открытое, хорошо продувается ветром. По сути это открытый корт под навесом. Совсем открытый, без крыши, тоже есть. Пиклбол и теннис.\nПриятный отзывчивый персонал. Есть ракетки в аренду. Можно бронировать корт заранее через зало.\nМного свежего воздуха!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Svetlana Tkachenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRCjW9T6hFc09zkae3_yXmlqT5GRhNU0Xt0tK4N88Pti3lew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Забронировали вчера корт через зало. Сегодня с утра мне написали и предложили перебронировать из-за сильного дождя. Это было очень мило с их стороны, клиентоориентированность 👍. Корт хороший и чистый, продуваемый.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anh mr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9EfqhiwMYGS7hDM404jlq5ut8PCtOMvxz9Ltb26cTrneKEHrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"8 sân cả trong nhà ngoài trời","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lukas Schmucken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxcJltbWl7b7Ztk3kKJBs64mNuJhWSTeBbP9xP6c0n8Tz2Zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Schoene Anlage, gute Preise und nette Leute. Und natuerlich Huda","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dang Truong Binh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJELUME_YRHbfvF3FJgG6dc7W66H58CSJusTxKgHfqworlJSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"","Images":null,"When":""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"4":0,"5":12,"6":25,"7":32,"8":42,"9":35,"10":35,"11":27,"12":25,"13":22,"14":30,"15":52,"16":77,"17":100,"18":97,"19":82,"20":62,"21":0},"Monday":{"4":0,"5":12,"6":10,"7":10,"8":15,"9":25,"10":32,"11":30,"12":32,"13":52,"14":67,"15":85,"16":92,"17":92,"18":85,"19":70,"20":50,"21":0},"Saturday":{"4":0,"5":30,"6":30,"7":35,"8":32,"9":37,"10":35,"11":37,"12":25,"13":35,"14":45,"15":65,"16":77,"17":80,"18":70,"19":47,"20":42,"21":0},"Sunday":{"4":0,"5":20,"6":25,"7":22,"8":27,"9":32,"10":42,"11":35,"12":30,"13":30,"14":37,"15":55,"16":57,"17":62,"18":42,"19":35,"20":22,"21":0},"Thursday":{"4":0,"5":35,"6":37,"7":37,"8":45,"9":47,"10":47,"11":40,"12":30,"13":27,"14":37,"15":55,"16":80,"17":97,"18":92,"19":65,"20":40,"21":0},"Tuesday":{