"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipO2ZRQRIzwepT44yVeDo178biHG2QFLOK7808F3=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipO8novlvOlYeyHCDPTZ221FzJpolqRXoOmOWlgQ=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOJibBGoyPUR951r2Ugs_30bMSzXMjX0IASOgHM=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipP-ElcWWfx5WUEjI4HXSxT6litVy0C6WnIufViP=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPEyJ9tCy6_wTB-DpQJ6rFaTLcb2n90O4WVOVSZ=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPFcP9rE1E9Ly1o7ucia2Kk7lJYH1gpd0IuuSWM=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPYgWwzRtLo3DkbxOQ7LdGtjI-ICBk6-Nd52C92=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPd9NgmLq9HSwDCgJR2XUhs1gcK1UeXqkSA99eK=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPr3UJs7BxSShC7LhwMk1Xw5i5gjo7vZGq4GvwA=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPxWS36vuHEFZdXuv77CUxcueGU8Y01vHzJ4D3u=w203-h270-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."],"Monday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."],"Saturday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."],"Sunday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."],"Thursday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."],"Tuesday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."],"Wednesday":["5 a.m.–11 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Honest Evaluator","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRTHjeBNz0rJxFJvTbab2HJqAOR1IbWS6aCHnECxlIsO4mMD8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Hot. Needs better ventilation.\nQuite difficult to play in the heat.\n\nThe dividers between the courts are quite low, often the ball ends up outside of the court.\n\nStaff are nice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Ferrer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpwvZGgoyGX9BZb-cpxI-00yW8w6TmlLrxGkjhxlD4-iC2uZs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place and super helpful owner they let me test out my new paddle for 30 minutes.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi7Sv6YZITfuoWtrXEQoGzkPKS9sIvkwnkrw5ygJfpO6mLO0NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my second review. The first one wasn''t all that great. But they have a new manager who is supervising the social play and he''s doing a great job. So, brand new courts, all very nice. All the courts are covered so if it''s raining we can still play. They have about 6\\7 courts. It''s pretty busy so I would suggest to reserve a court.\n\nThank you for your time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Keith Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2ktQBP_yimCf8n0fQr5aOJId9XoiNLhlBMhoXswJr0EijgiiI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a very good time at this pickleball court today. I found the manager very helpful and the other players very friendly.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Lw1Tj6zhLW7Rn7poLpgfGPA6MJu_PP_X2CZeUljPzjKzTZf_L5Z_FyT-UUjMNydGOhUVKiuLIfLKsQ378pgqPqOi993n2BwRrASW1O2YcVFJ5ogM1O7Q8oGuBl54uYvN5RJB_1HTjxmqe=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-30"},{"Name":"Débora Pellens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJZkrwEXhT2kN_ot1yAA9cKIYQpljHrtLbROYwj2kj0un9dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place is horrible. We came to play and the owner kept making fun of my friend because of her weight. Then he brought out a scale for her to weigh herself and started laughing at her. Unbelievable — I do not recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria helena Correa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBpsMNwy-hgH38YHO5fdB4pPVod7D-Xflwhqp6-rNJEE_yHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a deeply disappointing experience at this place. I was treated with clear prejudice and disrespect. It’s shocking how unwelcoming and judgmental the environment was. If you’re not a local or don’t fit their narrow standards, I strongly suggest you stay far away from this place. Discrimination has no place in sport — or anywhere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQfIs8m4PWX-84C3ETZr5k2l1nSMCCWQZgfbwzC-gN_on4FtkFJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have nice experience here","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0XbokKOcav_IbmgF71llAlEFNjY1R0HdZ9ReYOcJb-0IHwFWgQHs8anETZTte5atZQ0jMP58p06HRfKfYKvTwLXBczCGZ1Ebt7nLBf7mlmTetTKvx0pclLEbORQos_pdM4vjcaYBwdIDw=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-8"},{"Name":"Henry T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlb3PDVKyKTiXYCe7tN3KqvKBMA3cq1zqAIdS5UO8N7a1_mw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to get your pickleball fix, strongly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"4":0,"5":15,"6":25,"7":35,"8":40,"9":37,"10":32,"11":27,"12":25,"13":27,"14":25,"15":32,"16":35,"17":52,"18":50,"19":47,"20":42,"21":37,"22":32},"Monday":{"4":0,"5":35,"6":37,"7":32,"8":32,"9":35,"10":37,"11":37,"12":30,"13":22,"14":22,"15":32,"16":47,"17":67,"18":87,"19":100,"20":92,"21":72,"22":40},"Saturday":{"4":0,"5":10,"6":22,"7":35,"8":45,"9":40,"10":35,"11":40,"12":32,"13":35,"14":35,"15":55,"16":57,"17":50,"18":42,"19":35,"20":27,"21":27,"22":30},"Sunday":{"4":0,"5":32,"6":37,"7":45,"8":40,"9":32,"10":27,"11":22,"12":22,"13":30,"14":47,"15":62,"16":65,"17":60,"18":52,"19":45,"20":37,"21":32,"22":27},"Thursday":{"4":0,"5":32,"6":40,"7":37,"8":35,"9":40,"10":52,"11":57,"12":52,"13":52,"14":52,"15":70,"16":82,"17":87,"18":90,"19":75,"20":57,"21":52,"22":37},"Tuesday":{"4":0,"5":25,"6":25,"7":22,"8":32,"9":40,"10":47,"11":37,"12":30,"13":30,"14":47,"15":65,"16":82,"17":85,"18":80,"19":55,"20":40,"21":30,"22":17},"Wednesday":{"4":0,"5":22,"6":27,"7":30,"8":27,"9":27,"10":27,"11":42,"12":37,"13":40