o","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAH4cH2tcKR7zNmzC1nOrdPbKoopjft3S_BpbjPEhg_g4Nb6V-_igIAf30kKfFWXpEhCAON_-d44WAcFpJoBXO0XIks_4Otu54NC-Nh1cR9yNFuSgknuxL2nakW6pamAyXaJgi66LHG9cA3B=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHWct8nnwBn2nV-9uHtkPqce9xzjo0LwMuC5cNqo4cotJ1alsBHW7ANhSLIv4M0mOlM9AhugK2qWGHMuMqZprO4pPSb8gXnxvCUNN_84_p1s3ahCAZZv6F3-qx1PhcTfzMmPKFa48kLQIEW=w224-h298-n-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHwSaX1oVelElAY8lrcVlfUnBBwTXwp2ttsmA9YRacch6kaw0mcYeN04IIb0gcBddzGwLSIZzPg4TvrZSoA1k7r6505ZGzNlVBrYIFq0DrY7eZTDQztHLbKM5odr1dDo_k0QMyirUlClM4=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMVFr2hjhDvajNRCqbQQL_6Y9d4ulh5jeYxqWtu=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMvV5YFjoPu1yB0jRccsMClqhoTs1-GkTPqi24W=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMy1Ue6I80XoAV0g3EsSjqd5juSlhV4NTFUBIwW=w203-h203-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOaGpt7uTXD4U10n3_TPGVn_uEcEWC75XLidriT=w203-h287-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPt3W7_AlieXS4nN_m-2ua7F8RpAxz5eAiM2a1A=w203-h182-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Monday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Saturday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Sunday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Thursday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Tuesday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Wednesday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"huy duong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILcvyWYQu04PAXe6X-zEeW2NdN0ncEtceEcXu4MOCVHxQ7lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly and enthusiastic staff. We were a group of 3 and  they happily joined our group to game. Nice space, nice breeze in the main courts area to keep pretty cool. Only thing is if you’re beginners and hit the ball high the ceiling is lower in the main area. But still high enough for most, we only did lose a few points because of it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lien Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaAF7cGQx-Q4E_DrIIw1YSdwJSxFCGjumpaO9v0YNlccyXtpq4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"1 cụm sân :3 sân trong nhà , 1 sân ngoài trời\nTrần hơi thấp\nĐược cái nhân viên thân thiện, nhiệt tình , thoải mái, zui zẻ\nGiá ổn\nĐặt trên alobo đôi khi rẻ hơn .","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1zwXgYEKGh-51pFKFrMnPYVv-sjlYvqiEP81_ExbLLmVKJrb8dFkWbk7VXsiu_yT5U3D9w7lhuwYBRA2I7pzjlWfCrvQzUz472zt54fywKLQiSDoM3KYODZT3EVEH6CO9ostFxf1xLK-QV=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3DtHSLVz8BxlJ5HzJwx9ZDxd0sQdKaJiY-mR3YhxHjrVriTPxvdfpsueLxzj3h32YxZ383SFmlWfHOmmV2BbrOL5jhC2LtTzHovIEv8XDLF20eJtWRe1b0KbUe3_mb7oUHGnduSg_PT8w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MGCO4riU_2muRSnQVGf2KdhjoxlJdUx0Dk7JFPj0kJtyrCBE5b19OPoseUO8SsG-AhaSE1sWMDlqxQlaJ07uhRtWAFYu4kvvaBvM0Y7mHK4j2IDnP0xU5isDOgZBNRUzWHqeQgdOQaPs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36yF8bTVwvTnrfLHyZRQeowFUqJ9wy5AoS3ZPbCTPFJQLHWikBaNe1Xk6u41zktM5XOEgW9knnVt7ifRe333kDJZo6j4mz6G6PqsZi_Dn955kKIfeNnI0HekKn09A908iq_5Xi_z26x5Nu=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-27"},{"Name":"Ng Anh Duong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzuTIVrqf_VxDQYhRkuXggYFETkj7d7PbQGcN0EEZESHm-jCGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Đến sân này mn cần đến The Blues xong chạy hết đường là có cái tầng hâm rồi để xe đó r lên tầg 8 là đc ạ, nhân viên 10đ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"phương is real minh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9kT2rxmUkjcwTYmAprr0y9ofPy4HQ96L4hde8B34_MqfoARQSYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"sân trần thì thấp, không khí thì bí, vừa đánh vừa thở sợ bị nghẹt thở tới nơi, lúc đặt sân thì bảo sân này cứ báo vs bv dưới hầm là đi đánh pick để ko thu tiền, xún bị thu, mình đã bảo là đi đánh pick về đó bác, bác vẫn kêu đây 2k việt nam đồng đây khách xún trả mà, mình cũng đã bảo trên đấy nói 1 đằng dưới này nói 1 nẻo. Lúc đánh về với trải nghiệm vậy mình hoan hỉ để sân này vào ds ko bao giờ trở lại, giờ xún thêm vụ này nữa, thế từ nay là khoải nhé, thật sự rất mệt nhé. Em ko sao, sân và service nửa sao nhé khỏi đôi co","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3eek-VtDRLv77kCTWF1_wyoYjcLFiOP0vbzbhx36HtJmxb35VCKUxaLY9r50y2OzIdIcC1xLpE5pEHrfZYiD1OeUuzcG2uO3tTOGl9jr4ByhvBRjJDp655jKcn2ZodP60yRibxo4P9Lo05=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-12"},{"Name":"Liubov Denisenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPiNJbDeKSp_h60K6md9SMQ3LmjESHrGZMsVCQXuh9yvRRdlux=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Друзья, если вы так же, как и я, не понимаете, где находится этот корт, рассказываю:\n\nНапротив входа в Go есть бизнес-центр Vinh Trung. Заходите в него, проходите мимо лобби, далее заходите в лифт и поднимаетесь на 8 этаж. Enjoy:)\n\nКорты понравились, чисто, удобно, есть вентиляторы, мячи. Персонал доброжелательный. Можно купить напитки. Вернусь 💪🏼","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ngọc Thái 6637 Phạm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2AiMiyLuYMaV_CxxP5xVza39n60pT-Lu38qyEJKnZQO4agpc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nhân viên dễ thương nhiệt tình\nGiá ổn\nLần sau sẽ ủng hộ","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1UWNL9F0B_WgtGvGkaAIiyNJpSz02D1OxyYNk-e7PUwihrdQgjR7CHwhkH18E92NTDry-Vf6tiVc7pRthi-YIc-L51QPIQgUBn7NO8UuIaOpG3R66U4bMNYwXre8ceeeMge5nOUGKtthFG=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-1"},{"Name":"Ging Nguyễn (Ging)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8tJ5_zMTpz1BnNb8PCsNzP0vPVSKl9xOmcoqZoc_GgfgiudcG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Không khí trên tầng 8 thoáng mát, nhân viên nhiệt tình!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hiếu Đặng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMoxDagxsrU86i2mYcHH75HH7ZbdlBOWzToC6txTKrxRXevg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nhân viên nhiệt tình, dễ thương. Không gian thoáng mát","Images":null,"When":""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"5":0,"6":45,"7":30,"8":25,"9":20,"10":35,"11":30,"12":25,"13":30,"14":50,"15":70,"16":55,"17":55,"18":50,"19":75,"20":75,"21":100,"22":0},"Monday":{"5":0,"6":70,"7":60,"8":50,"9":40,"10":40,"11":25,"12":30,"13":30,"14":40,"15":35,"16":50,"17":60,"18":60,"19":40,"20":25,"21":20,"22":0},"Saturday":{"5":0,"6":25,"7":35,"8":40,"9":40,"10":45,"11":45,"12":55,"13":40,"14":30,"15":25,"16":15,"17":15,"18":15,"19":20,"20":30,"21":20,"22":0},"Sunday":{"5":0,"6":20,"7":20,"8":20,"9":20,"10":25,"11":40,"12":40,"13":50,"14":45,"15":45,"16":50,"17":45,"18":50,"19":25,"20":30,"21":30,"22":0},"Thursday":{"5":0,"6":30,"7":40,"8":45,"9":75,"10":50,"11":40,"12":25,"13":20,"14":25,"15":25,"16":25,"17":40,"18":50,"19":60,"20":75,"21":60,"22":0},"Tuesday":{"5":0,"6":40,"7":40,"8":30,"9":25,"10":40,"11":45,"12":50,"13":35,"14":30,"15":30,"16":45,"17":55,"18":55,"19":55,"20":45,"21":35,"22":0},"Wednesday":{"5":0,"6":65,"7":60,"8":45,"9":30,"10":25,"11":15,"12":20,"13":35,"14":45,"15":50,"16":60,"17":35,"18":35,"19":40,"20":50,"21":25,"22":0}}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral washroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Washroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Wi-Fi","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Onsite services', 'Gender-neutral washroom', 'Washroom', 'Wi-Fi', 'Free parking lot', 'Paid parking lot']::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url