sonb, '{"Friday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."],"Monday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."],"Saturday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."],"Sunday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."],"Thursday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."],"Tuesday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."],"Wednesday":["5:30 a.m.–10:30 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Pavel Strabykin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRkvJUZWhXrL9Xrmse6zZvft02PuCdjH_u_CP93wrSEhjiEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It''s probably the best court in Da Nang. Perfect equipment, reasonable prices, free rackets & balls and excellent service! The owners do this not for money, but for people. They really care about you: there is some fruits provided free during the game, so you can recover. Last time manager even gave us a box of branded balls as a gift :) thank so much for such an awesome service!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15v6PEaZg2LNLA_VZl_kdqdSwFsznSec6fI_LTyBhl52sHB2hpgEedQhlWLylNy-p3zMs4vrGkfGy29vcocB-uq44XuxSwQyxIo1lJebN_Y8FMc00mg_XShf7y5Ra4zHOnM8eDcTflu4Iw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KIKDkCNsi38lw5e5wbpgvgruw5s2J5GfRlwABuIhigJlpw16uUDL89_lLUdlnFmK6xSBWQiZg2w5GnJd7jeqcv8wPHiQdxEjt7ZrU2_dmCqLV-euEORssDC6Q5zBL-VtIf4deY4G6ryA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2tdn39oToY_WPVxTCOC2xZAWotUrdfI7zJ_e7_5MyO8Dtu5K_K0-4g-parZFWxnBoQzbWdJDq8VyOEGRLwRxHiBdYaU_V6OBP-tm99A0N8AXWcav-Iq2E9BXhOQE9drOh7VN3p_6vvUhd5=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-25"},{"Name":"Anna Belz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4nCNG5MHttTQUVF622r2-p6U9Q7D3IkRjPc22F2kTur1DUTwc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This court is more windy because it is separated by a net, not metal walls, we were there on a not very hot day, it was comfortable. The price on weekdays until 16:30 is 120,000, rackets s and balls are included in the price, the balls are right on the field, there is no limit on their number. The court is a standard size, comfortable. And since 15.04  the  courts are  separated by a net, it is really comfortable .There is also a fitting room, shower and  lockers. However, I did not use them and did not check with the administrator whether they are available to everyone.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0lKq_0sxJ1-GdaDiIffMplyFPJA5wyQX4DdvmapWsBasgTXNF8vfGjx6i4Z14Bp4aqjZg3hYvuKvUoTPSAFdCJSA-zmDh0yQPKrDncStj-iW6Gtah1MU2MES6tziDQ3Ll6E7Lv=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn32YnARgKjyUNuZjeKHh0_5-rF6z-_BVX-r3fdq7jKjvL6o76GwNXgVnSbZZElXmwoT8upHPcem30UgJ55stf5uvffpdgK_bCLXH503YHMIDjKMrxCosu3CpGGTV5lakt5Df7V2Bw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LYKNxNidHeAen18cmg1Mc9K5TxLYDmWBGLtWrWCFd4dpnSLS-kxiixU8BHqMKoDhGLZrGecL9osWW1Q7dM1y9_gEX0dBPJ1N_UXY2VNErmxPtbSD95wM1YpxfXRpeJ_gUcjiiLA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Q2UoQG7cxRVbwsr6SNL62k7GeinyVacD55aZHdPDqkvKQkmPX5eoAVpxxIuNmeKd6MFq03Qri7nCJRdiidV9vHUwKHEzdSiXLEcJK5yMo43GgveB34m6zrjMzEBvFTkqeiSBDKQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn02aeCgLP8keLPio_2RXAolPgimqlG_-5bZqUzQaeM4mXc1WSwpSE4eWzY61dSHvmmdNo5yN3hwP1kYbG60-zvHkKoYfIGCBjOLoqGVAMPZ_TPktmgGVgeZhnqr-tPFFxujQK0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2boQxD0MJCEEusygmAqcba9NwLvVnPvg-8k9ULX-4I8tOO6ewbQhxuDcGDp4w4a59LZujimdLkpwjNUde7LxAxWOOlhMgWcOpVvQ6zhcNotxiWGxkEliQE2SyxL4BoIBHSG2MurA=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-10"},{"Name":"Donna Gutierrez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3IT49ABm2bBncihtnmTsTjXe0WdNixPVdiOXhRcbcOKwTcCf8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Easily one of my favorite courts. Love the cafe beside it, the court surface, and the restroom is clean and spacious","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2CzSBCxKYNwbs9uWxDKeTbyfo4va8LyqvS35wnPZgjbTck1id6glNhgCvxGjLXfKmAMNBCxuz-0sCWbPmCTZkmx5yok744QBOmSq9aICUDRU_htQgWOlLqKlmrpdDq1nYk4qecOE9pMGZG=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3LgU7zo9VoLwkxstg4K8e5tz-Ds_iCu8-JXXkDL1TCEmvvFKTdS9o7R1-zw8dyKhUkil9XxmklHR1yzcSnqU1sNFnRZXHPwz29oakWwGzedG5O-ShoTPnnxQN0goHBIF9oO_We7ktWhVU=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-7"},{"Name":"Svetlana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoTW8_sNwkhGBXGv87ATUyVGvgcJe1asYXscksBf4Ru2YzNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this pickleball court! The location is perfect and easy to get to, and the entire facility is always clean and well-maintained. The restrooms are spotless, which is something I really appreciate. The staff are always kind, friendly, and ready to help with anything you need.\n\nThey also provide high-quality paddles and balls, so you don’t have to worry about bringing your own. The place itself is beautiful, the design and atmosphere make playing here a real pleasure. And to top it all off, they have their own bar with drinks, which is a great way to relax after a game. Highly recommend this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bonny Missy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB-jX8ChvYcguuWQryabknEqBMEIgX7lfQLkahOM0iZrMhHTCp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The court is rather hot after 10am. The owners and people here are just too friendly and hilarious There’s also a lovely air-conditioned cafe which we could hang around after matches. Cheapest and most fun court I ever been to :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Матвей Кострыгин","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxQrd588Cq-KNUH5_vkfFljyVfj7boIA1R75cCblWVKhOT9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good place. High-quality surface, cool enough even in the middle of the day, everything you need.\nThe only thing that gets in the way is people who enter the playing areas early, walk around, for some reason change there (although there is enough space for this) and this interferes with the game. And no one controls them. In all the other places I''ve been, people enter the court only after the previous players have left.\nOtherwise, a great place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"En Ka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqL82vI8cIw_vS1ICbfwNEa5F4yc-WAiZuba5nxVZlyFx94w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am a neighbor living there a long time before you opened and hearing you every day from 5am until sometimes to 23:30pm. Yes, not just 22:30 but as late as 23:30pm. You need to protect the community around you from the sound of it.\nPeople yelling and the sound when a bat hits the pickleball is going through the air and into the neighborhood with no walls to protect us from you. Every day. From early to late. Do something about this and build proper soundproof.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CELINA BROOK","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzkOZTNq_z19MUNtNyfszySS7hFGWXSiLSmlpTh7AuQRlS8Rp9Lg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent 2 court. Well kept. Clean. Covered or they even ask if you want it uncovered. They provide nice paddles and there are lots of balls. 120k drop in. After there is a perfect cafe right here to enjoy your cafe moui","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0__1vquigveReMpbX7YAbaWkZiieuVxHkUKFh_7mGWINvHCExLn-vSuIU_wT5RM40PSnCVZWMNTdHJAvuPv204dDd3348LryMke33y61uzQHmKUb1RorloKiacZ1ADNScbky8=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-26"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"4":0,"5":29,"6":31,"7":29,"8":23,"9":23,"10":31,"11":34,"12":36,"13":31,"14":31,"15":31,"16":31,"17":25,"18":23,"19":23,"20":17,"21":12,"22":0},"Monday":{"4":0,"5":25,"6":23,"7":23,"8":19,"9":23,"10":21,"11":23,"12":29,"13":36,"14":34,"15":31,"16":38,"17":44,"18":48,"19":57,"20":55,"21":48,"22":0},"Saturday":{"4":0,"5":27,"6":38,"7":53,"8":61,"9":44,"10":36,"11":36,"12":36,"13":38,"14":40,"15":38,"16":36,"17":25,"18":27,"19":27,"20":40,"21":38,"22":0},"Sunday":{"4":0,"5":19,"6":31,"7":46,"8":53,"9":61,"10":51,"11":46,"12":36,"13":36,"14":36,"15":31,"16":34,"17":38,"18":40,"19":38,"20":34,"21":23,"22":0},"Thursday":{"4":0,"5":17,"6":17,"7":19,"8":25,"9":38,"10":42,"11":48,"12":59,"13":55,"14":48,"15":36,"16":34,"17":29,"18":27,"19":40,"20":36,"21":34,"22":0},"Tuesday":{"4":0,"5":19,"6":27,"7":31,"8":36,"9":46,"10":55,"11":48,"12":42,"13":34,"14":27,"15":19,"16":17,"17":17,"18":27,"19":34,"20":34,"21":31,"22":0},"Wednesday":{"4":0,"5":29,"6":29,"7":25,"8":19,"9":17,"10":19,"11":23,"12":25,"13":31,"14":27,"15":34,"16":40,"17":57,"18":74,"19":100,"20":97,"21":76,"22":0}}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Onsite services', 'Credit cards']::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, opening_hours = EXCLUDED.opening_hours, reviews_data = EXCLUDED.reviews_data, popular_times = EXCLUDED.popular_times, amenities = EXCLUDED.amenities, tags = EXCLUDED.tags;
INSERT INTO public.courts (name, address, city, district, lat, lng, rating, rating_count, phone, google_maps_url, place_id, thumbnail_url, images, opening_hours, reviews_data, popular_times, amenities, tags) VALUES ('Sân pickleball Nam Hòa Xuân', '4 Đồng Khoa, Ngũ Hành Sơn, Đà Nẵng 550000, Vietnam', 'Đà Nẵng', 'Ngu Hanh Son', 15.9995552, undefined, 5, 1, '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/S%C3%A2n+pickleball+Nam+H%C3%B2a+Xu%C3%A2n/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x314211005f2534c3:0x8a0da1435deba4d6!8m2!3d15.9995552!4d108.2435891!16s%2Fg%2F11nhc6xzqp!19sChIJwzQlXwARQjER1qTrXUOhDYo?authuser=0&hl=en&rclk=1', 'ChIJwzQlXwARQjER1qTrXUOhDYo', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEdC221syTCpH5cp7D2izHClfTLZ57t5Sxy6xkwKN7lHgkHNTAWHgxyIlh8F1ziEd9EkdSw0nN7WrUu-isY8FwbSmHdpvt46gU1A5dmXrzQx0_dq-GuineuephPVwvzF8hXVU2JDt-rnGhJ=w408-h725-k-no', '[{"title":"All","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEdC221syTCpH5cp7D2izHClfTLZ57t5Sxy6xkwKN7lHgkHNTAWHgxyIlh8F1ziEd9EkdSw0nN7WrUu-isY8FwbSmHdpvt46gU1A5dmXrzQx0_dq-GuineuephPVwvzF8hXVU2JDt-rnGhJ=w224-h398-k-no"},{"title":"Latest","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHvYTePvtIpk0epw07uVkwVa1YTCSYvbhtQTpeoXXV6WiyXvov_wVW8gUzn0ETNIVBPPSARxLfoi3rniHekKDhGFvg0hcENmaerbqn2mm-W5wol0jmFNavWOAPbZjt_1FDm2fEg3XV7axE=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Videos","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFpUhJblhF0sYLxAOgzv0blXlGSqeVHfQm7UEqlGFFiLwPdstLLjk5ZNuJBXsLb-6zNcBtoOPypMxl3adsfyqfF2z5InR3UAokTV83UvyeH24hdwuT7GocQAQg3HIIjfFg1K4RgqbBNZOgE=w224-h398-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"//lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKB2L_6vct9l7T3bXiiEbEcIe5a5GOw-jM68vuq7onM5y_C2t4=s48-p-k-no-mo"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEdC221syTCpH5cp7D2izHClfTLZ57t5Sxy6xkwKN7lHgkHNTAWHgxyIlh8F1ziEd9EkdSw0nN7WrUu-isY8FwbSmHdpvt46gU1A5dmXrzQx0_dq-GuineuephPVwvzF8hXVU2JDt-rnGhJ=w203-h360-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEdC221syTCpH5cp7D2izHClfTLZ57t5Sxy6xkwKN7lHgkHNTAWHgxyIlh8F1ziEd9EkdSw0nN7WrUu-isY8FwbSmHdpvt46gU1A5dmXrzQx0_dq-GuineuephPVwvzF8hXVU2JDt-rnGhJ=w224-h298-n-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEdC221syTCpH5cp7D2izHClfTLZ57t5Sxy6xkwKN7lHgkHNTAWHgxyIlh8F1ziEd9EkdSw0nN7WrUu-isY8FwbSmHdpvt46gU1A5dmXrzQx0_dq-GuineuephPVwvzF8hXVU2JDt-rnGhJ=w32-h32-p-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFpUhJblhF0sYLxAOgzv0blXlGSqeVHfQm7UEqlGFFiLwPdstLLjk5ZNuJBXsLb-6zNcBtoOPypMxl3adsfyqfF2z5InR3UAokTV83UvyeH24hdwuT7GocQAQg3HIIjfFg1K4RgqbBNZOgE=w203-h360-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFpUhJblhF0sYLxAOgzv0blXlGSqeVHfQm7UEqlGFFiLwPdstLLjk5ZNuJBXsLb-6zNcBtoOPypMxl3adsfyqfF2z5InR3UAokTV83UvyeH24hdwuT7GocQAQg3HIIjfFg1K4RgqbBNZOgE=w224-h298-n-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHZ8KsmJeVklz-sCynwZvAwpEZcVIY1nMR4yCxGIXUJHxBmPwS3wItIqnk0h7eCqXoZ_WMusDwok3-OPJlLLREaFzt_7x9k9SxwNRHGKbyJn-eCrP0Os0mmFKoIAFSJjoQC7y0GS3VS9Fz4=w203-h360-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHq0BuIMeHmWWivdE8tdhi2D9Kck9cbVP4VrtwgKelWJNG7oqRfSwIR3qqi3koCu_LEvNJIK6y1BlaiGx4ZNsc1dWamV3mCMkVOphFqtasIaJwNZ9Oux-l4NNhY8C9lHmIbJmHwPY8_AN5v=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHvYTePvtIpk0epw07uVkwVa1YTCSYvbhtQTpeoXXV6WiyXvov_wVW8gUzn0ETNIVBPPSARxLfoi3rniHekKDhGFvg0hcENmaerbqn2mm-W5wol0jmFNavWOAPbZjt_1FDm2fEg3XV7axE=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHvYTePvtIpk0epw07uVkwVa1YTCSYvbhtQTpeoXXV6WiyXvov_wVW8gUzn0ETNIVBPPSARxLfoi3rniHekKDhGFvg0hcENmaerbqn2mm-W5wol0jmFNavWOAPbZjt_1FDm2fEg3XV7axE=w224-h298-n-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Thiên Ngô Bảo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKB2L_6vct9l7T3bXiiEbEcIe5a5GOw-jM68vuq7onM5y_C2t4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sân Pickleball Nam Hòa Xuân là điểm chơi mới khá ấn tượng tại khu vực Hòa Xuân, Đà Nẵng. Qua hình ảnh thực tế, sân có không gian rộng, thoáng, hệ thống chiếu sáng ban đêm mạnh và rõ, phù hợp cho những buổi đánh tối sau giờ làm. Mặt sân sạch sẽ, kẻ line chuẩn, cảm giác di chuyển ổn định và an toàn cho người chơi ở nhiều trình độ. Khu vực ghế ngồi xem bên ngoài khá thoải mái, thuận tiện cho người thân hoặc nhóm bạn ngồi cổ vũ.\nĐiểm nổi bật là cụm sân được đầu tư quy mô, xung quanh thoáng đãng nên không bị bí, tạo cảm giác chơi rất dễ chịu. Nếu hoàn thiện thêm các tiện ích như căn tin, khu thay đồ, gửi xe và cộng đồng hội nhóm mạnh thì đây sẽ là địa điểm rất tiềm năng của pickleball Hòa Xuân.\nMột sân mới, đẹp, sáng đèn, không khí sôi động và đáng trải nghiệm cho anh em đam mê pickleball tại Đà Nẵng. Hy vọng thời gian tới nơi đây sẽ trở thành điểm hẹn quen thuộc của cộng đồng thể thao khu Nam thành phố.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0AuU4H5tJBj67yeRE7RiS_wvpKlyXGePp-p1jjWm3Tm2umUguuk3yyXFxLIZlfh0Hzthy8uz13Yi4pAKMbxs5fnArdR-gx4uinUVq6tcsVxM06_ESzcpRSu9TuhYI1Z5vUgiXynm8kZbE=k-no"],"When":"2026-4-19"}]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, NULL, ARRAY[]::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, opening_hours = EXCLUDED.opening_hours, reviews_data = EXCLUDED.reviews_data, popular_times = EXCLUDED.popular_times, amenities = EXCLUDED.amenities, tags = EXCLUDED.tags;
