APNQkAHgMoJqob1cQ0jhto9RFaw1gh3E7AyWlVkvky2bYVca3uvGyp8dEtYKYcGbgR_PWHHCneKxrtX8FV_D740fI7HQjqhdAdK3pR8RZVvjL053SU4Rf_fmfzgXJRjvkaerMfuUwK56=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHn4zpoR6AewokS_Jkmib3WFYetCnbhVLD9XLxRlsaW19nFPcu6Wp1RAsukU2y4weiloS-mF_qRnP1F_kY94LROQRfxNUTi7tQPkVikoCrf-ZbpHzMHV0rPhKCos2zV3CBg_mrs=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMbvXWNJazbMd7uaH2Y_XefB84MeEr9BWlild4S=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNoWc-BDpWGwZjP4GTl1FPo4NwFM03irz67A4-E=w203-h253-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Monday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Saturday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Sunday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Thursday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Tuesday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Wednesday":["6 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdj_PR2J2_0Yf67YzunAjgdD7NEBgad8vRUMHDYr41GO86I4o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice courts! They have 5 covered courts as well as 2 outdoor courts. The walls are a bit close but it still great fun\n\nI recommend this place to anyone looking for some place to play some games","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0DlZbNeErXu962fntDCrB25u6IyqsSkeUQKbZ7P-YQC02rHTTyid2JQZLo5MAVaCk85cl5Blxntb1YKSwh-IDdqqF4gjeeN9NMtOmxBVe4yv_DxnvCxm2-B-z3DBGdIeJ7UceU9w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0x2N1Epqv6Jkz15C4Do1YwBmF5kzMp_CeLwrTTe2FgODrBA0W79po7AVfhks5oxTdTQd922RN2zxzRtqFXLh2_G_Aw1lYuIA6u_xyOC-Fro6nzJ8RJuEPBtZUARDNxkgJUeYk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1yZqQl90HYneuDZX61hKbew0MOHBN6C-4WaILLuKtYw2L89xOyIuIKsbzImO9xUidBcoHqblxOVkhmYoSKhJKbDuG_akdUFR_Q4paStAO1PCdqSEAEPJ5dZOBTL0dtC8Ntykrx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3RajDAgCRPsxoL-IpsiPbJgGGQ9mLTx0qBRuv9WA4ibvRNXpdj5AL5i0ZntjUS830oA9-UuecZMnEtmJxzmXif_zvfBOJlTmFeqawuxvDloL7I9ARDLw5eFqCcNfNdDO2v2OE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn39-2_NzfFSlhIVRjq0C9FVFZTaARYTZM4mNnTgsErZ0FMbbOkg5-I9M7B5JJ1NJALMv4xHvaujyPDGzJICo-c3bd1DCWD2eGEAidbUUYuMYJPXCD93IX6MwGCwRqzg5ws1zS1b=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0RUywUHtglryvjD0UWIVOtKqGlZXWrBlEFIxYY59UfMfZS8bEjhSdSkE4guEN0OkptXr1Jjj3Gnk7cQsrtw9NXPDHCKDuScyHP6leMNTSygFATSq1LHgvsZoU4jdMiAtNfEBPA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1q4WXB8cLcK2yuEaNDT2_NCMSqXtFKCvpDijKVP8SQmhMr4fev0Km-gWedZzURThnlXG5QTMk66Efh6BwYlMD9c5J8YeeMD9mSXi-aYQGgMzIAb4Z7WElnEk31ltzYsAk6fzHyIg=k-no"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Honest Hank","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEt19PN6bIFQU-z2PkZJK_VG2dEPG0j-lHdkqWJla9aphxqh8J=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Let''s be honest here, folks…\n\n…Fit Fun is here to rake in cash from the well-dressed crowd who seem more interested in showing off their cars and outfits than breaking a sweat. Good for them, I guess. But Honest Hank isn’t here for the fashion show—he’s here to crush opponents and dunk some balls.\n\nAnd that’s where the trouble starts. Fit Fun’s indoor setup is tight, and I mean cramped. They’ve clearly tried to squeeze every square inch out of this place, which makes the court layout awkward. Courts are jammed right next to each other and way too close to the walls. Take court number 5, for example. It’s practically unplayable— Go for a swing near the end line, and you’re meeting the wall instead of the ball.\n\nThen there’s the ventilation—or lack of it. Fans are either non-existent or just switched off, and it’s like playing in a stuffy box with zero air. Not exactly what you’re hoping for in a “Fit” or “Fun” experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tri Pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjp4UHnXPDekC5sRPU7LYBOdoECLN94ZGVaTdgp_KHG6kB8OWo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great for practice and playing picker ball ! I like the 2 outdoor courts. It''s great for opening tournaments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maciej Borucki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZAeSSi0lg3w2x8-ApK0w116Akzcb3PMOcA78lq13I40xByWZ_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice pickleball courts! They also have a shop selling a range of pickleball paddles.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ngoc Mai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMQaHgFJyTv8QImU9ZPMv-qsyBmf31G5g1fnUvGvPI0aFIrC1i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Le PhongVu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXRz1ElCpJSlL0Qef8QeUJr8tBt-0ITXk_wDst83XMJJ4Q0fg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rộng rãi, thoáng, nhân viên thân thiện, mặt sân ok","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Fy_jiITZT6KobSfwxM2USd_5M7R53U-c02-u8B4mngwcQkIaq7KMXl_p-HYQlJFJ1DNP4DsNr0gIXeJDXws1KUxy1RYz6efF9F9M7XOWNY0pQbqzbwO29Q0tGlniOTh6eifRmHmM2FhCU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22wKWoMx0DdVtclP6wzAVgYdDJ6pXo_8pBAyrApk3x2sWVqUI_qjAu8QwT8zU-a3zRG-t3NTVpmq0_40EAnck2c4kHA7XNbGtT-xB1OiqEyUbqFBYMbakD6piuPIcRKeP3yyU-w7-LXEOn=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-25"},{"Name":"Tùng Lê","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbeCRx-4rgJGputnqjbZkmhSroYW7H7gQnXq8xMmuoQBbfwL_t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Một trải nghiệm mới dành cho thể thao tại Đà Nẵng.mở tại 86 Duy Tân.hiện có 2 sân ngoài trời và sân trong nhà.Do mới mở nên lượng khách rất đông.luôn kín sân nếu không đặt trước.Phía trước có bán kèm theo các phụ kiện để chơi gồm quần áo giày vợt bóng....có sẵn căn tin bán nước giải khát kèm theo.chỗ để xe thoải mái.nằm ngay trung tâm thành phố.rất thuận tiện để di chuyển đến chơi.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0mw-9LwdlulEhxRflCgEOuv9Q23xiL__-gXrPxEf5FEvjH1nrLPUCDk27oYFWzSU3WHHRCKg2ArbFI2Zo5bkiMcRzXHrblraC5h5an_-1mjR_FLKTSYl3J6gKOsUZKP-C-bkFbKA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0fli0UCpWaxS7_P-0swrL_HCWsbXm5bEGIkjRFOxZWtVw2cnKiLKre-So35KR0_UigPQ7_FW3RpB-o5kNLPxguOa60XaKPDKeA_ZpU2MXjrdVfh9LEUCzh986Acs-hWTpdkDk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kXIlMmBI5f6Y1qZTBp53CRtJZGuaKEY2anU38IdyKESTbqvy6Fo5DfXbTffv3DRbccUHlZ5a6MJocLBQKO53UoLf_NKH3ljMQl61qbI7nZKTh4kzSRJ-psUugO0eyg__hsMI-ag=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn028bZfijoDhmrHFbFqL_35C-RZGj5OOUF_R9URjGoNGg97F5BtILdHZPOR0334g7N9SuqG2Rolim0vusbqOVeKSFfCspf8qVayFxo9SiXtu627gm_e0SPPfpizjW5zzfthFDow=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1vi3GfXMk_GIL0MVRe5c4BAL9yW3yarsuGSOhZpxVrpbbmdt_N-ujgniVNgUgpgQmBUPpttNvTzJPx29bZaBAj48NWhbaZPv5tNi3q_1apQprpWeCvt_lvQi0MVCS7jhgjrmACLA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3kp5Mx-VoiDohJCc12GUC4tZpX-97iTfQsxumd2ZLRUh4OKCLdx1SNi2v9JOoCtW3ZU0lvzN2iovF4WEni9Gij5j8ncx74qMUOaSM_EaUiPuf6sWn8vIT2iiDUSAECnLqDR-Dp=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fUKykfQ4Bcnaf6XOY0C5fn1nevPjBKWlMh56KURPlal2jBf7BlSz0QV0OHmcWhcwturvnmSUBudBfy8Iy4hzhI3PGRdFiAcM-aq2VgzrjBY-JJR7-uz1eixbCX1qRX5Q7NVcL=k-no"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"陳冠璋","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU3_64PsmP8Dl_2tI608s8q8piPYbl21p0-XYfQ6TG587YGy7V=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"📧 Subject: Inquiry about joining open play at Fit Fun Pickleball this weekend\n\n⸻\n\nDear Fit Fun Pickleball Team,\n\nMy name is Wind, and I’m visiting Da Nang for a few days.\nI’d love to play pickleball at your courts for 2–3 hours and possibly join a local open play session.\nMay I ask if I can join on Saturday, Sunday, or Monday as a single player?\n\nThank you very much for your help!\nLooking forward to hearing from you.\n\nWarm regards,\nWind\n\n⸻\n\n親愛的 Fit Fun Pickleball 團隊您好：\n\n您好，我叫 Wind，目前人在峴港。\n想詢問能否在貴場地打匹克球（Pickleball）兩到三個小時，\n或者參加當地的球敘活動。\n請問這週 星期六、星期天或星期一 是否開放單人報名或現場加入？\n\n非常感謝您的協助，期待您的回覆。\n祝您有美好的一天！\n\nWind 敬上\n\n⸻\n\nXin chào đội ngũ Fit Fun Pickleball,\n\nTôi tên là Wind, hiện đang ở Đà Nẵng vài ngày.\nTôi muốn hỏi liệu tôi có thể đến chơi pickleball trong khoảng 2–3 tiếng\nhoặc tham gia buổi open play (chơi chung) được không?\nXin cho tôi biết liệu thứ Bảy, Chủ Nhật hoặc Thứ Hai có thể tham gia với tư cách một người chơi đơn không?\n\nXin chân thành cảm ơn sự giúp đỡ của bạn!\nChúc bạn một ngày tốt lành và nhiều năng lượng! 🌿\n\nTrân trọng,\nWind","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IkotOzTHGkZeqgt1h8ZOMZa6TuQmnzrOW9f05JOwRK4HtCEec3duZYWuTcZVkPuYBhddM_NDHL7Nl9jRtIpKHtR2ZL1gdVHGmJPM62qAOA3-_XuC3Sjv3t8sGMxeionR5if3N_i3Vzesu=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-4"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"5":0,"6":47,"7":38,"8":42,"9":38,"10":52,"11":52,"12":52,"13":47,"14":47,"15":66,"16":61,"17":57,"18":47,"19":47,"20":42,"21":42,"22":0},"Monday":{"5":0,"6":38,"7":47,"8":52,"9":47,"10":52,"11":47,"12":33,"13":23,"14":23,"15":42,"16":42,"17":28,"18":28,"19":38,"20":47,"21":33,"22":0},"Saturday":{"5":0,"6":38,"7":42,"8":47,"9":47,"10":38,"11":42,"12":52,"13":57,"14":61,"15":71,"16":80,"17":95,"18":80,"19":61,"20":33,"21":23,"22":0},"Sunday":{"5":0,"6":23,"7":33,"8":42,"9":42,"10":33,"11":28,"12":28,"13":47,"14":61,"15":57,"16":47,"17":47,"18":28,"19":23,"20":19,"21":14,"22":0},"Thursday":{"5":0,"6":33,"7":42,"8":33,"9":52,"10":28,"11":33,"12":28,"13":33,"14":38,"15":38,"16":42,"17":57,"18":90,"19":100,"20":85,"21":47,"22":0},"Tuesday":{"5":0,"6":42,"7":57,"8":66,"9":61,"10":42,"11":23,"12":14,"13":19,"14":33,"15":47,"16":52,"17":57,"18":57,"19":47,"20":33,"21":33,"22":0},"Wednesday":{"5":0,"6":66,"7":52,"8":38,"9":23,"10":33,"11":23,"12":28,"13":28,"14":42,"15":71,"16":66,"17":47,"18":28,"19":28,"20":28,"21":33,"22":0}}'::jsonb, NULL, ARRAY[]::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rat