elpful. She made sure everything went smoothly and always greeted guests with a warm smile. Her positive energy made my visit even more enjoyable.\n\nThank you, Kim Thanh, for your great service and cheerful attitude — you truly represent the spirit of Furama Resort! I’ll definitely come back again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dennis Schmelz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7XA8guls78CbAy8PA4MB0MYIr7K6_-dnkpcH1E22C0ViXdQgf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First pickleball experience with our private trainer Són, it was a lot of fun. A mix of tennis and badminton, really enjoyed this one hour with my wife.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kim kneipp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIm9npgxekhI7sATFBvMfxcCpDH0fITyjto3KFA09KvcGQONw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mr Hai was so attentive and helpful and even joined in to play pickleball with me and my sons. He’s a great player! Fun for all the family","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chloe Georgia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXQDvKUEb-JtO1sA36puJTsQ0d6Byn47ppaoGJw73l_9mQzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a good activity during your travels, so much fun","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hoang Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUajZWMQvxiNbAu_XDlCwtCztFbwhnFKP7gkUygp0oss6WW2Isd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice courts and staffs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1kIi1IPRHo5MTeuCRhjb8lKFq2Pm3_GV9GMfagp6ALqXW_EdgimfuA-PKicNKWpdIYBuNmackdymQFQpJfWcsTQxXTMTcewERYDfOr8LW7QbZdPihCLUD551FcMuCkvicGlw3hTyvGeOw=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-10"},{"Name":"Raymond Dissinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuIRKiofBD4LKE0UQm2Nec0E4INedDw5UjWtJij6n94hmEwKfk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So much fuch my first time and very easy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phuong 