=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hi vince\nThank you very much for your lesson we have a great time at your court\nHighly recommend this court have great location right in the city it take only five minute wark from old town. Court with cover roof you can play even rain","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0BnMjZODzHNK0b6Nfjoas_dWEbooi-yvGrtz7H4kR6dLTi-z465a6bQE90BlH_rpC9QVdjZIavzmKYOpugYGpa2WLYSaWH1uAm6NGbn-KQuQRE9B2G26t6Php_sHU2mp_hWVab=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FTaniRC3K4VMDxBUFP27HNjTiYmA8gRt89kI9WqT6PQ7Upy4qqayVDjCd20KVAUSttnUvpqUjQtU55caQrT1OHli6Lw0ZFsY0BiuNxouPhr9IFCplYyJ1u0d6ggdDnfkpLsFk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0tJrPFGC2oPqmCP0JkV3eBt9BblU0QNeoJo4PMt17lSixv55jooHfrF737vlyy9uRwWLKwldSINMHHuHHeVLi2-GbLuquzR9v2HKnde7v1j4RqJO69XMSA9YccYMuhEGMg57gp=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-2"},{"Name":"Tom Buckle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWz9FfQWXIrruGH7l4n8VeBR4ilI6MwJ92EGh3vVu-DZPVS74yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A main highlight of our trip. Very accommodating staff and courts in great condition. Rackets and balls are free. We went twice, and would keep going back if we were in Hoi An for longer.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xkvxtT8JAimVOpslzdvcluZr4NJeSNfm0SSgFhj_b889AfUMMPtIG_62P_G3eUOA7fwIp5lyLu4pcrZWa1HNE9vFxaCBmz7il7eJUYmEqyE8guMyluFgzaAS1SpuM4bI0pEg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ACdnwjzbW9RUCNi_RIet5e607_ppKZhfPRe6pV8ZTgjKroxMILu2nA59zPVJ1Uxc_xmI3YgQPc-28qzPnAF-zXGKDHDBoIPv-EIxpApLyWuO8v9QN3Etwp1gHZyt2CuvEX1_z=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Steven Vetter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6vnV4oc6w-nZma7vKw5Fue-rwGhqnJ4Xq1XhhyPEAUnnKfUW6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first time playing pickleball!  Hot Kitchen Pickleball Hoi An - Sân Pickleball was a great experience! The staff and regular players were super friendly and helped us understand the rules. It’s a fun and accessible game for all skill levels! The price was very reasonable at 150K or 180K VND per hour for four people, including rackets. Highly recommended!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3am2YtyUI7sacyFoUuJvW-hZlDveYtG-kPSZdjJ2D8QKMX9V4U1dXxYY5qyiYbKS-H624UcDgqalY5GGrgR_Sh1bB3JH2jIwCmQLYN0LNDCDBMrUtfIzzxT12zZotn3HwKXpY=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-23"},{"Name":"mason parsley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3cLJXWbpHI-BJtaspL4UoOvHGKkA_fRajl_j0AZFoeA4cyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hot kitchen Pickleball Hoi An is the place to play!\n\nThey have the most inviting court I’ve ever been on. I showed up as a visitor and left as a friend. They have various refreshments including delicious homemade coffee.\n\nWant to take a lesson?\nTheir experts have got you covered.\n\nDidn’t travel with a ball or paddle?\nThey have that too!\n\nWith the new roof you can happily play rain or shine.\n\nWhether you’re new to the game or have plenty of experience you will enjoy Hot kitchen Pickleball Hoi An! 😊🤙","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn35uP3LzjVGDEFZDEM3mxFv4qAkF2V2g5_Ab3tzk_a3R0nkc4wZ6nhI7Li8BYyN7y0GLVXLFM85r_ICLbLPCnP0PR3ByyB8u7pA2du_AkKpiu-wmIgqzMOmy-AmnFGwSWj6WtKP=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2aJ8zmrXJGdWWnbaTzdgCdqK-wB5hzTrwPzc445uEcwUaTlXv7Nbc2Ip5iJHGVE-nkSYb1Z1deKxva13tbJy6zB0e_kDR_T0bq_C9Z_YycmlmVKdn8mBwt5fjamBkNGQa_4-dR=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Eliot Stutt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWt1bVLQ0fRhWRAcWZs-JXRmmhx4H7BhpzemmbYhTmfhbyWdQiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very new and clean facility. Paddles and balls are included in the price, very good value for money. Would come back again but unfortunately we leave Hoi An tomorrow.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2oVCRg3FWfasCTA_PywnS_cGHZmVIi2Q5Nm-Ctl0anlHFH_i8MPAUEZAka95SECvKuOX1V7NNzxG2cZ8g--1g_jUK2pk109TOdm13_nIqH9vcD_AMqSw_ueprQT5IiMwc6FT1r_Q=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Meeli Einpalu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv5Vg1ZKivIcPzQorQSIC7u9u6fGHdd2NkS0qFf9A0TU_xmu5JLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice courts, polite people, can play raining. Recets and balles available.","Images":null,"When":""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":{"4":0,"5":86,"6":100,"7":46,"8":26,"9":20,"10":46,"11":53,"12":46,"13":40,"14":46,"15":46,"16":66,"17":60,"18":53,"19":60,"20":73,"21":73},"Monday":{"4":0,"5":53,"6":33,"7":33,"8":40,"9":60,"10":66,"11":60,"12":46,"13":53,"14":53,"15":46,"16":46,"17":46,"18":60,"19":46,"20":46,"21":46},"Saturday":{"4":0,"5":66,"6":93,"7":86,"8":53,"9":26,"10":13,"11":26,"12":26,"13":33,"14":53,"15":53,"16":73,"17":66,"18":73,"19":46,"20":53,"21":66},"Sunday":{"4":0,"5":33,"6":40,"7":40,"8":26,"9":26,"10":13,"11":20,"12":13,"13":6,"14":6,"15":13,"16":26,"17":33,"18":53,"19":73,"20":80,"21":80},"Thursday":{"4":0,"5":46,"6":46,"7":40,"8":26,"9":40,"10":46,"11":60,"12":46,"13":60,"14":66,"15":86,"16":80,"17":60,"18":40,"19":33,"20":33,"21":46},"Tuesday":{"4":0,"5":80,"6":86,"7":80,"8":73,"9":46,"10":46,"11":66,"12":60,"13":46,"14":53,"15":53,"16":60,"17":53,"18":46,"19":33,"20":40,"21":26},"Wednesday":{"4":0,"5":53,"6":60,"7":40,"8":33,"9":40,"10":46,"11":46,"12":26,"13":33,"14":33,"15":66,"16":53,"17":46,"18":33,"19":26,"20":20,"21":33}}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral washroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safe space","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Onsite services', 'Gender-neut