i03twnjnGxpl0xKsYj6oHwhd4xsekg0uWYPcO5ATG7ARnYRF5yTc3DAw3KnUZ2YA0glTcCKNoagr7RQ=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHrLI8vGsZgWzPJEu1HIPMRxol_PNJjNuU5k9HwkF15TYrydf77ZIHZeNqiHsXF_dox95oSiY3AwgrKs5_zopECq6BUGoCD9r_sAZ9oVfwQNuj57hq8V-7DQ0qcZ8vdaiAo6kfi8kA28Tn-=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHujaXKI0GhuraBrkl_0OZyUaby2gsP003VJvGDNxyYN_AJ7V06CKPpK1yRdpySjmaLP4bIDQ1WBmDLXqEetjf5_Ww70f4YU5dAxuhZ2orwqhUswB1b3PK35gOidv7TfUFvfh8FX1peCs1Y=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHzcmaJ12OolIsCuF-NVLiM8N39ccQz4JvI-d2F3-FOE0jtej7bQsaMKi3rrw3H2WmvgO9qJjbl-Wu2eok636Noub35XaQ2X2P-c1REEhGThBeFJ8rqgMw0PZ7ypr4ikSryOMtCtrmA_sK5=w203-h152-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHzcmaJ12OolIsCuF-NVLiM8N39ccQz4JvI-d2F3-FOE0jtej7bQsaMKi3rrw3H2WmvgO9qJjbl-Wu2eok636Noub35XaQ2X2P-c1REEhGThBeFJ8rqgMw0PZ7ypr4ikSryOMtCtrmA_sK5=w224-h298-n-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Monday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Saturday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Sunday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Thursday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Tuesday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."],"Wednesday":["5 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Allen Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd2Z4ymQvwgaYNEv_ZVnEWD1yb302xFlVYyMqYQ7ArcasBGAPG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to go to and play. I came early and was trying to see if anyone was willing to play. The local worker said that he would play with me and we played for a bit. Good games full court and skinny singles. The facilities are shaded and good prices to rent a court. I will be back.  Highly recommend!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_6DNDq_ve2PfIylGDpXGmOLHwAkLMlfoUFSPbblwBdCeGHO7Y3xF2D4baul1KmwQmbMl9_KZ_Us_agFlQ00ozw7DKeaRBemn5EXXLI-H5jzM7Q735bgnw-Po3r5gEEX640zZ2bw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Dfmxk5fjcTTszts7-U6LXviXDC4oaEdEOt5IJjpP5uQe84a-5TB2zpWVR5e2XcwWhX6Ej0jUCE_225KudWJC4KK_XhDXXeOgOnHpl4cRzJlTHjP25JeeSoClXl_mZ354OZ68=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-25"},{"Name":"Christine Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpZqw1K2DoxMC26n_WJknixZSABZHVsw5OWqpSsAPAvHZRGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a wonderful place to play pickleball, great surface and under cover. Floodlights for play in evenings. Our friend who lives in Hoi An invited us,we had a brilliant time.  Friendly people and you can hire paddles.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1VK4ngBrOlTGDhDZ5s4tXRHQShIMJgu5yaFz5LGEY3ABd_QD0e6nDBKe0BR8wbHYiCJfC0RkAvnAzvDCYzf7Pnsd19_wrgW7C-c95eZNflOEHrwRFAz-pmjgOYnEaxFzj_azM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Hx8KCe0xjfYUPyqKx0jGEXbImYTLajNp7TYx-S03-Vz1oXZyrxLRRWq7J8C4-eqB6ZHvvXFRm22NjCUh1OcrtMQR3qFVX2pct_PqsPGbtaytqQ5NzhNx77HZYf7hZ2rzuZMRa=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-26"},{"Name":"Jay See","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiNHL9gtNYvcIyBf9Z8DbpYS0BakX1AxXPfN-OPkkf4W3cItul-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Second trip to Hoi An but first time playing pickleball here. Very nice courts which opened in Feb 2025 (1 month old when I visited). Spacing between courts is generous, all 6 courts are clean and there is an option to open or close the roof. As it was a Thursday afternoon, it wasn''t busy until 4-5pm onwards. Another selling point - it was inexpensive as it was VND 100k for the hour I played excluding paddles and balls (extra 50k).\nWould happily come back and play another game, you will be looked after by Bao!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15rp3_UAi8U5bQpBKSSX1G5IE_B-BixunkF5VRv1Pr8O1mhAlNuPnkZpYtXJTj3Y4uPHaNE_xFWZsY5oK96dk1VJySMLMxfiUjxxvnsLiMEQd4BAUGu_3qCty2by0q-0qkxTeX9w=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-29"},{"Name":"Freddie castagna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo4aoIgHKN9W7z2bSiWXRA3NrKdzMkseczkev5XwsX1dTFig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place really nice courts and friendly workers","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn30KU-cUQQhD-9hE9KJLYPNcaoaHWiq4-F34TTlb4AFGHgtK7EZER8PIcg4poUgUHYz1VaHtaETK_yjFWNkmV_5vDmGk7oV9HRe4DZM8Sjl_HfE_IXdZPncjJ4L8gIxMN7fpptgBg=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-3"},{"Name":"Evo''s Challenges Evo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7FQKSmHbpFd5UG4Py-JxYU0XIKkOM2IxYi38EWARsM1OKpDXS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loads of fun.\nFriendly staff..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tuấn Tăng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkEbn5OOfqGtvMLU-d1jsbz3UXC33jIQ0wWjwtj-Jp-Gk8e6HpeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sân chơi cho người đam mê","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2WSBt0slPo7nCBgVoG0TUxsZRyiVyaXXTCdG2PNNOBRnVrAb7LTYMlWPqc3V3lU2BMy7BLA-meG-xxohjo7ojEM9VUHkiAIz65bB9xoUU8zD7jxw1IyjTRDMXn1dBNNhjtnBmhWPznduXH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3F0Ab-TME_T_McmnnAIWtOdxrfuPg1A1a9hNE6MM9ho7gUDYl5wpbFS-XZ0eJsNqJ0ISKHKu8OTuD-wHgyHYfHgswckLqu9IL_y2wyvm3rUk3Lx7ULZttSbN_sIfzMAUhMbi2jUlspktbi=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1tE6jvw13ha7v-smvsJ7nE9gjs5U-Ac2hNSHADVHc7QZ13HI_6IzCXeQ-R5iBR0hxHJAS0UMXiwHawa9n09wCw_z4sJCFrSyeNEC0HN5ky7kteqV5lf91MgRWwj5SE-wWscejZhrZnMkir=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn26uBlcklJKL-bIwLK08_cNoLo0O-OpElFS9RR84wLTAJ7n4GaHEPWkZK9xE_N8Ln8kiAT81JtYq3ZbsM-N55TMKUOlVs2zT_83fHwHVoqhKnbOi3YYf4W5cQnqyQ0EN0-2cXM75HBrO7SS=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-9"},{"Name":"Dominic Tony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWd-68AkqNdI4kM3LtoejMFC-OSph1n5ugLA4FG6y3_l3RW8rfjJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sân có mái che; 6 sân","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn393jpjS0BLD8vHREBuYm_HrAcidyG-d9OIh-tjEqvMDgyGVY7A2lT4ir_HsUld9Q01k6-4S7Wz