Zwen_7ECK1HL0RiyyXXyjiZO926WU06SwZ2JJTHTYs41RLS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My partner and I went and played pickleball for the first time this morning and we had so much fun! The court is new and clean, and the owner is so welcoming and friendly🙏🏽 We rented the paddles and practice ball and it was really affordable. Plus such a great workout! They invited us to come back and play again, and we’re really excited to join😊","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YkRzgarSYlNu31__IIRdcyvNSGo6hPSfeZB-LMauKLl98Xl9gaawpnJyA3Y51F3vKSDIKFNeusjLRz_tX1ccUbDpZm1XTkdMbD7SxfdUPyevCjY2MZYdhe91FItsqAtNXEWqT=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-5"},{"Name":"Sam North","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxjb0ZIdiSHftI0s4PWxuOdPMFh0GLnDqqLuf2SnE0Xo76xx9-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little pickleball Center. 2 courts, friendly owner and locals, cheap court and paddle hire.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Calvin Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmz5Z3n5c03myDYftjHnO4Na_RwARxK4_4NEZe7Sjt28aUMA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chỉ có hai sân những luôn đông đúc người chơi và rất vui, các bạn nhân viên ở đây rất thân thiện, giá rất hạt dẻ nữa.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0sFgbSPL8eQEhWwehweifjOHq-dvjAl-ksv1FqZxj_gA3RmoSLSJfoTLwfN00q52oNWkfZgE66KsDmGHl4Q7sA4FIE421YYD-IfOuJsG5ujAE3gcwPkzEdtCw0BtyBl4xES5Z6FA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1OlOXIfjss5GeIfQDcFEFXFM5qqnSd1FKUGCKAibPS59TO8-uVyIPXWLxPbR5jvoPtm3tetzQUDM1PSw85J8ACdLCkc9Q25fTYQh6EFrYBRs7_jhLz_kgPq9P3zRTHivKbQCZm=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-25"},{"Name":"Thuận Trần Thanh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWxXqf_RkuORk4EJDIzz46iK-VVd6OaINafIHk3IJYKw7N4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sân đẹp. Mặt sân mịn, sơn kỹ. Khoảng trống xung quanh sân rộng rãi, đánh thoả mái. Chủ sân vui vẻ, nhiệt tình 👍","Images":["htt