 p.m."],"Sunday":["5 a.m.–8 p.m."],"Thursday":["5 a.m.–8 p.m."],"Tuesday":["5 a.m.–8 p.m."],"Wednesday":["5 a.m.–8 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"medium_nice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFDYo77BGcOj1gVOxIdDtk4K7d8Tmgm8RwulDHbG7MSsWJSIje=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic pickleball court! The facility is well-maintained, with a clean and professional setup that makes playing here a real pleasure. The owner Quinn and her husband are incredibly friendly and welcoming, making everyone feel at home. The pricing is very fair, and the community is a great mix of players of all levels and all nationalities, creating a fun and inclusive atmosphere. Whether you''re a beginner or an experienced player, this is the perfect place to enjoy a great game. Highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2WQee41k9WySYrxTBpo3gSI96JgDIicMpQH3eA8ceHNhC7Kor4dTJSa1_HY8ZYrhTVAJsKhC05nxsn3NpWD3rdc_OJPiNAnGjD_ZRxnj3WUiHVH-1SCgQl2ONdW9YRC1MX405p=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1O7xJ9JsdHw1sppgcUa3GUpLEO8JK1f0zdce5IkvzZnkfewCu6iRIdi0FZg8KH3FqW2CPcHd0VkJSipL3Ro0-NwxfOfTC7Cyub__0-1k0o5rhubIx1I11SlintHs0y_LN_O6jchw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LMYPCim45yeudsYRSb4NcPlAv93_nZwxGE10s1Qo4NKBRCtnBvpaiDm-AIEKF2GDE-kL1qsMCmGwkM9VSj_NVCcjXmfdYcRod4IECkeSNIwMfkzqYNIVxikyoHHuuqV1QZe4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xbPhADPMtRKToT6R93WztBp15ZFPrzjFlnFUSRTZZWVgmVn9pNJqm_UPpibkLr_UvBTjRJLCrcjiZuO_Vcv5wUSLvvDK3zzkFYmYNIrM9duwfagg9p_uITlv4Ir-9aYx5u4XS7g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2WjZrtf-Svwc9FpFJywVpzTNmby0ilT8XpOxe9YY_FMU5nnjiulWw-YQXg7NaQrh8Ks3h9cu-zqVn9Y-QnitJj5Qs6vRqqDjYyuiNz3DWnu_anQUMHXmmSoOedWHlvrg5U9EwQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Wa8kHp9s70dqNP-0LjCpBaHYG8RUpnn1pCqNMtV3tE87o1Db7PIyDuUv66xZeiyMioxvJ9fdChiT9FVmOSl6gUas0NiIJ09lPuZwRDBrRmGkGIODqkihtTy7tcK3kBP_7Uh4bvQ=k-no","h