":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPHTqKhwCRCkvHnkvoiQ_U0fHeBx3f1IMGAAVOd=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPQUnd4r-Mm6Yz41uOcKktb3DtDWlaJWdZMnmtF=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPRF_-N5Tx-Bdq2DVcZLhLzFaOHS3zlf662_kcd=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPRTGkclxe9aIyeW1a-5Xm1bBCPR2-ZpbBtkk_u=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPW2X55e-UXJKTVj-4EoVawYVy3Oyg4wGznkVOs=w203-h304-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPZ7hf-MmBgCLrm89SQ2j8ynjJDT1Tikhl7VVwl=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPaLiDV6Z9wobOwT7ipYDcLQzq_0z0Q8CmCSADn=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPbaPIU_0bU_24adCQ5BcOEJSg5pVae0r2WTcf4=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPlwDEX05dsBV8Dso-dqPAmM_jTCysktnniVEPU=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPmvUVPZIVCBVbFI8XIF6mMJHBo1jiV532YZ97j=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPoA8BISo97ouZyo_F0bLAifXFJABlhL5OGjavM=w203-h135-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Clinton T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJx1W03Scg1UabhA4KOuZNTo-BgGfUFMXjgeiGc9ikpKppGdw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"1st time playing this sport. Heard all the hype and decided to give it a go. Was on holidays in Da Nang and found this place next to the hotel.\nJust decided to ask if I could join a social session for beginners and was welcomed with open arms. Session starts from 7pm-9pm but this place closes at 11pm and was lucky enough to meet the owner of the facility , Jazzy.\nHer English was fluent so she helped with all my questions etc….\nI paid 50k VND to join and 50k VND for racquet hire. Relatively cheap in my opinion to have a go.\nHad a few social matches and wow what a workout. Place was not air conditioned but it has a retractable roof opened to let in some fresh air. Of course there were fans blowing everywhere!\nPleasant experience and would highly recommend if you ever wanted to try or even play there if you are a regular player visiting.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ZdqbjYXlrjJlNL9Ff0Wbo5QfMgHHsgTT4dzdhdjocf-XUCLgrnChbeHXqfANhPfSnSJrlLJWDRRUvUC5axxBtgUEOvHojBViuCk6wwa7sOwA1G6EQ4LvXbhSmfxupFnSM0ttOs5JpD9Q3=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1m_W0QA1qCED1SGLmeASNyfOWhUDmiJmPSo9NNcYUjpkqBFS36glk_jKT9uWU7L34fGNXAOMSGEjliD_YSJphzvgeux0AA206Zk38daBNRCkNYW_VYZ7Sqsk5s82vIGSHhcSH9ngmsK_VA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YsWwhngEVhdk7liH2Gcof8xt0QSYOeIgf04srYxOEf0Z6nkHE0KtarDDt_qSR2ThaCMtQhTV0ad6WqCDn3y806LbDJNicMUTln6yMY66sROrelCeFUN3-xdigS_-143FDYPf4kaI6EmRA=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-24"},{"Name":"Alison Chui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaSNxXqa7A3Vo6KuDAq-JIl7urEXejRUxejp4UJ02V1STb6PgR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The courts are spacious and new! Rented rackets and ball for a one-hour game. They have fans but still sweaty bc of the weather. We enjoyed the visit!!! :) staff is nice and we didn’t have to start the game at 00 (fixed hour) since there were vacant courts. Fabulous experience! Good deal for hiring a coach too, if you want to play seriously :)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3WDCgd93t9QzRsa9abrmClhXzB6deC-MkbJK6EFAHbE1Er0YpGCoSJzmiEtKYvIVmYzZBAt0K3F1EpIlry5xkY6s6IwHsBOcNQRkQT9u9CRIa_4Nxz5dVStUaao3Rda5hxXv9z_KpzQgR9=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-29"},{"Name":"Vincent Ferrafiat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZBcMB40pWk-S8hUnUlsVfFP0vly9HXk5agy492NnKJxkXqg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot to play pickleball in Da Nang! The courts are high-quality and well maintained, making every game enjoyable. The owners are super friendly and always welcoming, which creates a really nice and relaxed atmosphere. Highly recommended for both beginners and experienced players!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EcPdGZHERkfEG83WpDO9oORN_m2xhDZr3fSlPzCP71JUXT2QclKzrPbhZzPIL54PfHDpvGNb0uq-yqd9pIXsCEQncITnIwk5B9wC4qfBB_iwaNiVq_1f_5N2wpCg7p22cP1T_qzC3lBvv=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-30"},{"Name":"Adam Menzies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJno2OABcD2rtOkdIh2WETT2Nha5HkjfSdUQsiFsTXSVn_Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice facility! Only drawback is that the lights turned on and off a few times during our court rental, so we had to stop, draw the sun shade back for light…and then the lights turned back on 10 min later, had to close the sun shade again. Obv the sun shade being open caused us to get roasted and super sweaty lol.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyo5rQhFd0D5TGsc-SdbCZcfl4cffhY0dkRDJBJqX9GRAXipM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A stunning sports venue just 5 minutes from Da Nang’s My Khe Beach, surrounded by luxury hotels and ocean breeze. I felt totally relaxed in this beachy, laid-back vibe.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9C55547MCgnwFC-TviKOkKzovVg1gqOvlL29GZ247Vmd0tlzq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this place — it’s elevated my game for sure! The owner, Lha, is fantastic and always so helpful via Zalo whenever I need support. I also really enjoy playing with Thong; he makes every session fun and competitive. Even when the socials are light on players, they always find someone for me to hit with, which I really appreciate. And it’s pretty cool that Court 1 has instant replay via video — a great touch that makes the experience even better. Highly recommend to anyone looking to improve and enjoy their pickleball!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"베트남 10년차","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMS_9YLgbIgHkkcNGOu1EAaeNQdiXBxn8zeIbtjUL_-hqycA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Comparing to the new facilities, the worst service. To the people who considering to come here, don’t. You have a plenty of choice elsewhere.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3DFqg9rnZPp_3kxybBAYTyriCAZjqwEEyitixguGoRf9qleCYYqJFM-xyMRknSe5YpMqKAniyRrq8Kgpsmhm-XjujjYFGu1ZZ6vZs_aHQl3hw3CHTkqQku57iO2t0P8QEsFej_zuNowwE=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-23"},{"Name":"Count Monte Fisto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjbbJJ847y0EOnVI4b6NOV6iQ365jcb48ds_ARVV7jEVW59vM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a nice time there, will be glad to return","Images":null,"When":""}]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral washroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safe space","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Onsite services', 'Gender-neutral washroom', 'LGBTQ+ friendly', 'Transgender safe space', 'Free parking lot']::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, opening_hours = EXCLUDED.opening_hours, reviews_data = EXCLUDED.reviews_data, popular_times = EXCL