o"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHnQdm0fDJJPHHFq2k2Q-iPDA8dHe9jkU8V-PAtpitB8uFBW4aC52FWOEsjIsm8jOuzfQHnK-6e4hZWXlhcNPpR8W73jAxYxVrVm82X-dWzF_kGvGHw4LocZTfqwpPYB_Fuspnzm_AJRZxT=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHsSPSezBAuvxI-mPegPaTi2JYZUEambIUHHg8hB3Rdc3tm4kxF9li6MS8elrMX-UFeTGyz3rJZGnSdch5q8-OQzeY0IGyN55T_6jO7RJyMgLMUZUgJFdTyjf15N_KBwaH1PnPu_soI1GGX=w203-h270-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMD68hhYUGwCVK2wIRkIYJq2AK2sxrRnRhv88Tg=w203-h304-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMPKV8XXNRNs3NsbeNbfwQJCtwcZXxoNxCti-iK=w203-h345-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMdPPSUhWlu7VrHnRhxkbM6cN6-k02pxhQ-gQPd=w203-h345-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNAkQs8hQHNtyUrwwgaMjLiQ0mgE6MbmUrsk53X=w203-h288-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNHMzXEwfSyBqBRsgOyhgHNxJPOoJ0ZWjtaX-Bf=w203-h304-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNvCL7w8jO4ngyaMgKFNxRPGMg4Gx6mt0mtmwO5=w203-h304-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOB-GBuq0jh4iKJKVMo37v1TgmK-e0KMznM7JCt=w203-h304-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOa14DyTZn8enqNzzvTcenWJjssilPpH8P6iVLH=w203-h203-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOhW0b6apjKGzGVVOqta_hUBkZBpJOrAhoAIBvN=w203-h114-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOoVuGVaqxi5PizTGJwJBnJAmEIMXlFxFoQNaZA=w203-h304-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipP3eELnPTaypqAnyqZ1yIr6UQoTiXTmW6M2j_XQ=w203-h135-k-no"},{"title":"Photo","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPAD8Qc187fMMMNPEUsyaYRBroxiSJPMM2YsuEj=w203-h114-k-no"}]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"Name":"Дмитрий Новиков","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKx9GLp1u3rDenf2UYySx9zx4Cdx5ZDiBvzc0b8cvtTFLE8U8a=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I arrived at the facility today at 11:15 to rent a court, rackets, and a ball for one hour. There were at least five courts available. Two administrators refused to rent a court to me and my friend.\nI recently moved to this area, and for the past four days—from November 29 to December 2—my friend and I have been coming here in the mornings without any issues. Today, we were denied service. I tried to find out the reason, but no one even attempted to explain it to me.\nThe administrators were completely unprofessional and incompetent. Dear owners, please train your staff to work properly. Besides losing money, you are also losing respect from tourists. After the refusal, I simply crossed the street to your competitors—“Pickleball hợp thành phát”—and spent my money there. Think about it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Max Leslie-Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOZkXuNQYxatODyQ228-Him2veo8QNe_zYFPQZgglFJmYBanc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Disappointed to say we had a bad experience here.\n\nTurned up on time for our pre-booked court and they said there was a tournament on, so we had to wait 30 minutes to play with no warning from the court.\n\nThen after 1 hour 30 more we were kicked off the court (the owner was there too for this conversation) and they made us pay for 2 hours, even though we only played for 1 hour 30 mins.\n\nWon’t be coming back\n\nEdit - when you moved us to another court, this was our suggestion not yours, also we suggested that we move to another court later, that was also our suggestion. You also didn’t let us extend our session. And no apology from you at any point. When you make a mistake, please be honest in your reply.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shivansh Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVFHswrifWORhv7M9-nhfh1M0mR1rZsfSA-ijgyy6aKdztoPa77Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing courts, international standard 👌\nNice and spacious, good seating area with fans. The staff is also very nice and friendly","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1W7pEBsDvT7Oz8dC1pRRjWLTUlhzUEKb2I4MkrvjZ6TeOu94_iOREeOz4z9Z7zahY_Fy3xjQh282k-vDx0m30bJfYmKQ7JGWlg5joCklX8nY_-10cF8lEFJxpfj7cV103SJOO1Aw=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-31"},{"Name":"David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi7Sv6YZITfuoWtrXEQoGzkPKS9sIvkwnkrw5ygJfpO6mLO0NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was surprised you were closed. Hope you are opening up somewhere else. You did a great job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dana eagland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdzU3J056KIzIynJRnPDwX1dnXXaID6NxWu7moJI7YBvLEYEfS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They have 3 courts for social play newbies intermediate and 2.7 plus\nAfter playing on 2.7 plus I was told to play on intermediate along with all other players I played with.\nThen on the intermediate players played endless games I waited 30 -45 minutes\nI mentioned this to organisers and he said they are playing 2 games ( he was not really interested.\nThen I see players i played with on the 2.7 court playing again ( they where same or lower level to me .\nI felt unwelcome and seems like what should be a good system badly organised and a boys club for the ones that know the staff","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Duy Đặng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjKiUWwaY7lT8tyMIXkIraGcDn2sJefrT1IAU5s6ujGOanVcb7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best pickleball court I have ever experienced","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thienphuc John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxV51W0n3Jr7LC5DXkq1PLcxD3ng7gPPMG4eXsh2XPHW9poQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thế Viên Hà","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7L2VcPmTlcWIIZ1Dq4hku9herXtqfOBtZjtmZZl6GrnJYw57v=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sân có đường pit xung quanh rộng, mặt sân ngon, quản lý nhiệt tình vui vẻ. Social có thiết kế chổ gác vợt. 5* đáng trải nghiệm","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1HfCI78cWx_Rm2NJXDJFcNlhJGqEWW9d6BnLK9s8fBPxZAy8tXLqN-WulRTkn9SBIbOIz9UML7LHlasE2EjwSvc9pBS-PG4p76xSYndGriyyTsW5TgCebqvsQquqTyLDjdQaOmD9se6795=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-28"}]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['Free parking lot']::text[]) ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, opening_hours = EXCLUDED.opening_hours, reviews_data = EXCLUDED.reviews_data, popular_times = EXCLUDED.popular_times, amenities = EXCLUDED.amenities, tags = EXCLUDED.tags;